{"tid":2304732,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中國又贏】美國衆議院星期三表決法案 限制中國公司於美國交易所上市","createTime":"2020-11-29T05:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T22:03:48.000Z","uid":138409,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"77d14b5526cada0b81145e45d8e8e51193d533ef","tid":2304732,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:19:50.000Z","msg":"Holding Foreign Companies Accountable Act<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/senate-bill/945\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F116th-congress%2Fsenate-bill%2F945&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoRwKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=3d18bcc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/senate-bill/945</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-11-28/house-will-vote-on-bill-restricting-chinese-firms-listed-in-u-s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2020-11-28%2Fhouse-will-vote-on-bill-restricting-chinese-firms-listed-in-u-s&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoRwKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=a64df9ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-11-28/house-will-vote-on-bill-restricting-chinese-firms-listed-in-u-s</a><br />\n法案規定<br />\n假如外國公司<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">無法證明自己不受外國政府控制</span></span><br />\n然後又連續3年唔肯畀美國嘅「公開公司會計監督委員會」（PCAOB）核數的話<br />\n就唔畀嗰間公司嘅證券係美國嘅交易所上市<br />\n<br />\n而且有趣地<br />\n講就講「外國公司」<br />\n但係啲條文突登 提 中國共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如法案要求份審核報告一定要公開 例如 有冇共產黨員做董事<br />\n<blockquote>(4) the name of each official of the <span class=\"gold\">Chinese Communist Party</span> who is a member of the board of directors of&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n(A) the issuer; or<br />\n<br />\n(B) the operating entity with respect to the issuer; and<br />\n<br />\n(5) whether the articles of incorporation of the issuer (or equivalent organizing document) contains any charter of the <span class=\"gold\">Chinese Communist Party</span>, including the text of any such charter.<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">而目前嘅問題在於<br />\n中國公司一直唔肯畀 PCAOB 覆核 份 審計報告（但係其他50幾個國家都肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n最近瑞幸咖啡單嘢又搞到一鑊泡</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n法案將於星期三以特快通道表決<br />\n限制辯論、唔准提修正案<br />\n通過的話要三分二議員在席同投票<br />\n顯示<span class=\"gold\">法案有跨黨派支持</span><br />\n同樣嘅法案五月時已經過咗參議院<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留意美國證券交易委員會目前亦都度緊規例<br />\n可能令到唔守規矩嘅中國公司退市<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴同百度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6469c169261b7a986ef65c7b68c72118e858341","tid":2304732,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:20:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d6dd4370247e1e1dfbe73657f9376bc191057697","tid":2304732,"uid":33263,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:21:46.000Z","msg":"咁基本上所有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />公司都要退市<br />\n因為理論上所有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />公司都有黨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522cbd43b59676cfae56b3248363528cfeb60064","tid":2304732,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:50:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"862e7483d653bf9f885a7a1bb1e1f45b146a5eb3","tid":2304732,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:52:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a4f5bbc104aa89be748d3ac97d65824590c4eb6b","tid":2304732,"uid":161011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T06:00:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1446b9883